@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state Waiting
state Active
state Expired
state Archived

[*] --> Waiting

Waiting : entry / rate in waiting state
Waiting : do / check current date
Waiting : exit / activate rate

Active : entry / rate activated
Active : do / maintain active state
Active : exit / check end date

Expired : entry / rate expired
Expired : do / mark as expired
Expired : exit / prepare for archiving

Archived : entry / rate archived
Archived : do / remove or archive rate
Archived : exit / no further action

Waiting --> Active : start date reached
Active --> Expired : end date reached
Expired --> Archived : one year after expiration
@enduml
